{"word":"G3191 - μελετάω - meletáō - mel-et-ah'-o - Imagine","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μελετάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">meletáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mel-et-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Imagine</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவலைப்படு, சிந்தி"},{"paragraph":"to care for, to attend to something carefully, to practice"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3199 - μέλω - mélō - mel'-o/3199\">G3199</a>; to <i>take care of</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>revolve</i> in the mind: - imagine, (pre-) meditate.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}